  "title": "Assistant Restaurant Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lead and support daily operations at a Japanese sushi/omakase restaurant located at Robertson Quay, driving exceptional guest experiences and operational excellence.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee restaurant operations to ensure smooth service delivery and high customer satisfaction</li><li>Manage and motivate the restaurant team to achieve performance goals and maintain service standards</li><li>Coordinate with kitchen and front-of-house staff to optimize workflow and guest experience</li><li>Implement and monitor compliance with health, safety, and hygiene regulations</li><li>Resolve guest issues promptly to uphold the restaurant’s reputation and customer loyalty</li><li>Assist in inventory management and cost control to support profitability</li><li>Collaborate with senior management to contribute to strategic planning and business growth initiatives</li></ul>",
